{"tid":375650,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人研究西洋魔法？","createTime":"2017-08-26T15:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T02:56:25.000Z","uid":131552,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca0af74febcc0120771bb826b5f33301d9d63c51","tid":375650,"uid":131552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩先發現到e樣野，有冇巴C對西洋魔法有研究？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/ldid9yw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2Fldid9yw.jpg&h=0cb5f383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時了解既野都唔係好清楚，<br />\n係WIKI copy D基本野比大家認識下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>魔法，是一種在現實中尚未經過證實的，催動並控制能量的方法，大多牽涉具神秘色彩的力量或是行為。<br />\n廣義而言的魔法（包括下文所提及的仙術、妖術等）多為依附在特定信仰體系之下，為信仰者所相信，能夠引發超自然現象的法術形式。<br />\n至於狹義的魔法則專指歐洲文化中所認知，冠以魔法之名的術法。<br />\n尚未被證實而亦無神祕學說法的超自然現象通常被歸類為科學的範疇，不能稱之為魔法，而一般中文慣稱之&quot;魔術&quot;，雖英名相同，實則屬於戲法，在此亦不討論。</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">想買D魔法蠟燭鎮靜下心靈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"0e73c3c25992e1a8981bdf6fc83a26fc649e3a2d","tid":375650,"uid":140626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"疾疾護法現身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50de42cd208e70d406e42025a72386b709552b17","tid":375650,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn-static.denofgeek.com/sites/denofgeek/files/doctor-strange-2-benedict-cumberbatch_64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-static.denofgeek.com%2Fsites%2Fdenofgeek%2Ffiles%2Fdoctor-strange-2-benedict-cumberbatch_64.jpg&h=c24adc8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea7b292a08c2a91803380ba5aa82546b0c08082","tid":375650,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":