ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60950ee83ba26ce6ec5d467004c70d5d9ad562f9","tid":375650,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/035122_b20c9168edc63ff9de6c1fdfa3e1ac51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F035122_b20c9168edc63ff9de6c1fdfa3e1ac51.jpg&h=cced284b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d087f7f9854338f23b8635a181c9f06e01326e9","tid":375650,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:00:33.000Z","msg":"以前讀書果排學校好興研究茅山術,不過冇人真係識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw樓主唔好咁揚唔係比人燒死就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282cca888e0fda3c79beb33957ecb51ab653f3e2","tid":375650,"uid":131552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前讀書果排學校好興研究茅山術,不過冇人真係識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw樓主唔好咁揚唔係比人燒死就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我所睇到嘅魔法都有分正同邪<br />\n白魔法就係正面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n白魔法，又稱白巫術，指對人有益處的魔法，人有正面影響，或倚靠神（未必是單一的神）的力量而進行的魔法。通常這種魔法可以治療疾病或異常狀態，或用於達成某種心願，是一種企圖以超自然方式影響世界的魔法。比如：求晴、祈雨、驅鬼、破邪、除蟲、尋物、招魂、使不孕婦女生子、使沒有感情男女相愛的巫術。與白巫術相對的概念是黑巫術。一般相信，黑巫術是用來控制人的靈魂的，而白巫術則用來控制人的心靈。[來源請求]"},{"pid":"9ab875351b35e6629cd6f1e2256c2276b06df70e","tid":375650,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"正評比小櫻"},{"pid":"7da645ba3e7449dcc45dce7052c2ab370cbadd8a","tid":375650,"uid":70217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前讀書果排學校好興研究茅山術,不過冇人真係識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw樓主唔好咁揚唔係比人燒死就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我所睇到嘅魔法都有分正同邪<br />\n白魔法就係正面野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n白魔法，又稱白巫術，指對人有益處的魔法，人有正面影響，或倚靠神（未必是單一的神）的力量而進行的魔法。通常這種魔法可以治療疾病或異常狀態，或用於達成某種心願，是一種企圖以超自然方式影響世界的魔法。比如：求晴、祈雨、驅鬼、破邪、除蟲、尋物、招魂、使不孕婦女生子、使沒有感情男女相愛的巫術。與白巫術相對的概念是黑巫術。一般相信，黑巫術是用來控制人的靈魂的，而白巫術則用來控制人的心靈。[來源請求]</blockquote><br />\n其實心正則正，心邪則邪<br />\n吹到仲有灰魔法添"},{"pid":"80e0864dd5cb47aadf1e876c149d4bedcbc4c89d","tid":375650,"uid":138738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"呢排學左幾個 black magic<br />\n有興趣大家可以交流下<br />\nbtw心靈感應真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9f7b9d11949d1b38ca32d74eed6274f58a00fe","tid":375650,"uid":131552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排學左幾個 black magic<br />\n有興趣大家可以交流下<br />\nbtw心靈感應真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1807a7abc93a6d3092d8bfd79cb1be5663c3ff69","tid":375650,"uid":28506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"Magic always come with price"},{"pid":"dc3d5bbb6e2ebc4098160f4a4b3e33d421a36498","tid":375650,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得魔法係d邪法 咒術之類<br />\n類似中國厭勝之術之類</blockquote><br />\n到底厭勝之術<br />\n<br />\n係討厭個厭定係讀壓力個壓？<br />\n<br />\n點解cctvb轉晒做到壓力個壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511f063f27b8922be722f6cec288bf96378b3d86","tid":375650,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得魔法係d邪法 咒術之類<br />\n類似中國厭勝之術之類</blockquote><br />\n到底厭勝之術<br />\n<br />\n係討厭個厭定係讀壓力個壓？<br />\n<br />\n點解cctvb轉晒做到壓力個壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/n